<subSubSection id="D7CAA79C524760EC8B143D5ADCAFD42B" pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="male genitalia">
<paragraph id="0FA9A5E65AF8515A79F67CFEFAF0E992" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Male genitalia.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="44260944E075952A9AE1BD36D1B01835" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
Pygofer (Figs 
<figureCitation id="667DD82D82F4D9DBB9CD5AA016F36ABA" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="2C8B6C1530BB102E5712DF202525EF57" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">14</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="F1FB4E56E57761D3345D8D139CE64B52" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="C167DDC66B1299007FD0A65466484609" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">17</figureCitation>
) symmetrical, gradually narrowed towards apex, with sinuate anterior and posterior margins. Pygopher with internal sulcus and almost parallel lateral margins in ventral view. Anal tube (Figs 
<figureCitation id="ED679F8625FFA1F92587BF1788932A2F" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="C40532B6832305CFD60796175FD44713" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16</figureCitation>
) in lateral view, hand-shaped, anal style stout, lateral lobes distally shorter than anal style, basolateral side with a long finger-like process. Aedeagus (Figs 
<figureCitation id="11405C0E71D91CE7DE5BFC8D8FDF6F37" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="5763839670C03F1304E151E7B4840C87" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">15</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="DE714BF7183A66383C02F83E370C45EE" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="FDF5A01DB9E28FE72265F003E15EBD28" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">19</figureCitation>
) acuminate apically, with tubular periandrium, lateral lobes swelling on both sides, surface beset with scale-like productions, ventral lobe slender with an acute apex, dorsal lobes with an acute and a nearly rectangular process; in ventral view, base wider. Gonostyli (Figs 
<figureCitation id="4EDCB126A05BA955F64F7A61BF429EFE" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="C545E3D9B72BF890D83D3B449EBA1B53" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">14</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="0C539A18E6A2C4F9F6F7D509085BDDB2" captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16-18</figureCitation>
) divided into two parts, inner process curved apically, tapering into a process; in lateral view, outer process convex, bifurcated nearly equally at apex, inner margin with long setae; in ventral view, divergent, duck-shaped.
</paragraph>
<caption id="8EF0922809C8906E2A6E7B58BEF2165D" doi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197" start="Figures 9–19" startId="F2">
